<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p class="geolocation-title">Experience the joy of a traditional Christmas in the Alps or the Rockies. There’s no more special way to celebrate Christmas than to head to the mountains to go skiing and snowboarding. Enjoy a truly white Christmas by spending the day on the slopes before heading back to your chalet or hotel for a splendid Christmas dinner. We can’t think of a better way to celebrate.</p>
