<p>Of course, our <strong>Partner Hotels</strong> will be all in the party mood and all our hotels offered on half board include Christmas gala dinners - some even offering special breakfasts as well. And we have a good choice of <strong>self-catering apartments</strong> which are particularly recommended for families or groups of friends who want to 'do their own thing'.</p>
